===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Raihan (Masters)}}
Raihan forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Duraludon}}, {{p|Flygon}}, {{p|Gigalith}}, and {{p|Sandaconda}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. His Flygon and Sandaconda are capable of [[Dynamax]]ing. Raihan became a playable sync pair on April 28, 2021.

Raihan has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, [[Legendary Adventures]] and the [[villain arc]].

